<h1 id="installation">Installation</h1>

<h3 id="step-1">Step 1:</h3>

<p>Add <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">gem 'jekyll-theme-fica', '~&gt; 0.2.0'</code> to your <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Gemfile</code></p>

<h3 id="step-2">Step 2:</h3>

<p>Add <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">theme: jekyll-theme-fica</code>, if you run it locally and</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">remote_theme: Involts/jekyll-theme-fica</code>, if you using GitHub-Pages to your <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code>.</p>

<h3 id="step-3">Step 3:</h3>

<p>Run <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">$ bin/run insdep</code>, if you download it on Github and</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">$ bundle install</code>, if you download it on RubyGems.org</p>

<h3 id="step-4">Step 4:</h3>

<p>Run <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">$ bin/run server</code>, if you download it on Github and</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">$ bundle exec jekyll serve</code> if you download it on RubyGems.org</p>

<h2 id="reminders">Reminders:</h2>

<blockquote class="prompt-info">
  <p>Before publishing the site to github-pages, replace the varable of baseurl <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">baseurl: /jekyll-fica-theme</code> in the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code> in <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code> .
if you have brought a doman remove the varable <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">baseurl: /jekyll-fica-theme</code> in the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code></p>
</blockquote>

<h1 id="customiztion">Customiztion</h1>

<h2 id="customizing-_configyml">Customizing <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code></h2>

<p>Fica Theme will respect the following variables, in your <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code> file:</p>

<div class="language-yml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
2
3
4
5
6
7
8
</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="na">title</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="pi">[</span><span class="nv">The title of your site</span><span class="pi">]</span>
<span class="na">description</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="pi">[</span><span class="nv">A short description of your site's purpose</span><span class="pi">]</span>

<span class="na">socials</span><span class="pi">:</span>
  <span class="c1"># Change Involts to your full name.</span>
  <span class="na">name</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="pi">[</span><span class="nv">The auther of the site</span><span class="pi">]</span>
  <span class="c1"># it also be the copyright owner's link</span>
  <span class="na">auther-link</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="pi">[</span><span class="nv">Link of the auther</span><span class="pi">]</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<p>Change the links of your site header:</p>

<div class="language-yml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
